320
00:26:01.166 --> 00:26:03.965
The air is trapped in here.
We're safe for now.

321
00:26:06.498 --> 00:26:08.565
Keep an eye on the support frame

322
00:26:08.665 --> 00:26:09.865
- in the rear galley.
- Yeah.

323
00:26:09.965 --> 00:26:12.964
Yeah? Look out
for any signs of buckling.

324
