and the black box.

348
00:27:28.694 --> 00:27:31.227
Help will be on the way.

349
00:27:31.327 --> 00:27:36.027
We just... We just wait it out.

350
00:27:36.127 --> 00:27:39.927
But we will need oxygen.

351
