Madison said
she would check them.

354
00:28:01.959 --> 00:28:04.292
I could kill her.

355
00:28:04.392 --> 00:28:07.526
Think you're your little late
for that. dude.

356
00:28:07.626 --> 00:28:09.958
There was a man

357
