429
00:34:42.271 --> 00:34:43.937
Yep.

430
00:34:44.037 --> 00:34:46.104
No sign of anything.

431
00:34:46.204 --> 00:34:49.937
This is Sierra Oscar 10 to base.

432
00:34:50.037 --> 00:34:51.280
